\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let us consider two poisson distributions with random variables 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{1}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{2}$
\end_inset

, such that 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{1}\sim P(\lambda_{1})$
\end_inset

